titleInfo.title: Note from Lewis Pelly, Agra to the Government of India

physicalDescription.extent: The item is written on the verso of folio 54.

mods.abstract: Note regarding the return of letter No.115 Political of 10 September 1873, from the India Office to the Government of India, which had been transmitted to Pelly with letter No.2621P of 30 October 1873 for information.
